<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要拿我的<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />當賭注，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們來玩一場遊戲呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />你贏過我，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就把這東西送給你當獎品，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我要玩～！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">現在先不要吧</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這才對嘛！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那在開始前，<delay20 />
要先說明一下規則嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">麻煩你了</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我已經知道了</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是喔？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼<delay20 />下次有機會的話，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我再來邀你吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay8 />那就好說了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="NpcShuffle" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然如此，<delay20 />先趕快把牌洗一洗<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay20 />到公布答案的時候了！</message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺厲害的嘛！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />
是你的了，<delay8 />拿去用吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎唷，<delay20 />還真看不出來你這麼厲害！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
你就拿去用吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次是我贏啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然很遺憾<delay8 />我不能給你禮物了，<delay20 />
但還請你不要太沮喪喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我輸了，<delay8 />不過玩得很開心哩。<delay frames="40" />
下次要再跟我比一場喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不用灰心，<delay8 />
下次有機會<delay8 />再來雪恥吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好啦！<delay frames="40" />
那我們就<delay8 />趕快開始吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你聽好了，<delay20 />這可是一場認真的對決喔？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，<delay8 />等等<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的持有物品<delay8 />不是滿了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣子<delay20 />就算你好不容易贏了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也沒辦法把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
帶回去，<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還是先去整理好再來吧！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那麼，<delay20 />你可要聽清楚啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡有<delay8 />四種卡片，
