<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你呢，<delay8 />就要好好猜想
我抽的卡片上<delay20 />到底是什麼圖案喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你真的猜中了，<delay20 />那麼按照約定，
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我家的<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
就是你的啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="NpcShuffle" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />那就要開始啦！<delay frames="40" />
首先要把牌洗一洗<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 05 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />抽好了！<delay frames="40" />
