	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很抱歉，這是<delay20 /><tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來是你猜錯了！ </message>
